relation: Just a pic of Pokey and Picky looking off at something far off in the distance.
Ness and Paula standing over a Sanctuary spot making a bridge with their hands. I swear, I had some kind of meaning behind it back when I drew it, but I forget now... Oh well. Enjoy.

Inspired from a video of mock-fighting I watched a long time ago, although I'm pretty sure I messed up the position somehow. Oh, well... Enjoy, and revel over the fact that Poo is probably more limber in his joints than you might initially think.
'The fight will be starting very soon. Good luck to you both.'
The final dance of the night, and the Annoying Reveler is the only one without a partner. And just look who his rival is dancing with.
